author: David Fischer
title: This adidas Ultra Boost Uncaged Comes With Multicolor Speckles All-Over
text:
Visit the original post to see all 5 images from this gallery. 
Today we can give you a first detailed look at one of the most interesting upcoming adidas Ultra Boost Uncaged. At first it seems like the sneaker comes with a simple black Primeknit upper, sitting on a white Boost outer sole. At closer inspection you actually see that it features subtle multicolor speckles across the entire upper. A great little detail that makes all the difference, while keeping things overall clean and minimal. Look out for a release of this new adidas Ultra Boost Uncaged in the coming weeks, with an expected price of $180.
